00:03:35.919 --> 00:03:39.110
In the story, the writer
and Borges are presented

00:03:39.110 --> 00:03:40.330
as the same person.

00:03:40.330 --> 00:03:43.040
The writer is a famous
author named Borges,

00:03:43.040 --> 00:03:45.040
although he's curiously alienated

00:03:45.040 --> 00:03:46.460
from this aspect of himself

00:03:46.460 --> 00:03:49.520
and so writes as if
Borges were someone else.

00:03:49.520 --> 00:03:51.240
But the point of the story would be lost

00:03:51.240 --> 00:03:53.126
if the writer were not Borges.

00:03:53.126 --> 00:03:55.610
Borges could've written a story like this

00:03:55.610 --> 00:03:57.830
about some other author,
real or fictional,

00:03:57.830 --> 00:03:59.770
and I suppose a possible interpretation

