is that he's doing so,

00:04:01.090 --> 00:04:03.870
that the fictional author also
happens to be named Borges

00:04:03.870 --> 00:04:06.270
but I don't think it's a very
plausible interpretation.

00:04:06.270 --> 00:04:08.950
I'll assume a more
straightforward interpretation.

00:04:08.950 --> 00:04:10.150
So we have two identities,

00:04:10.150 --> 00:04:12.863
the author is the writer,

00:04:12.863 --> 00:04:14.870
the one referred to as I

00:04:14.870 --> 00:04:16.510
and the writer is Borges,

00:04:16.510 --> 00:04:18.123
the one referred to with Borges.

