00:04:27.450 --> 00:04:29.550
These relationships are
perfectly reasonable

00:04:29.550 --> 00:04:32.010
and familiar ones to have
to people other than oneself

00:04:32.010 --> 00:04:34.970
but some of them are a
bit odd to have to oneself

00:04:34.970 --> 00:04:37.823
and some of them are
impossible to have to oneself.

00:04:38.750 --> 00:04:41.340
So the writer says he knows
of Borges from the mail

00:04:41.340 --> 00:04:43.260
and sees his name on a list of professors

00:04:43.260 --> 00:04:44.970
or in a biographical dictionary.

00:04:44.970 --> 00:04:46.680
There's nothing mysterious

00:04:46.680 --> 00:04:48.950
about one person knowing
about another in such ways.

